{"tid":1631860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"風向撚請停止吹風 只有你自己眼見既先為真實","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:36.000Z","uid":33786,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b4de78173a7e6a3e9c57c1114cd5477e0483eb97","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"連登已經比一班舊有五毛進化成風向撚 / 民意撚 去意圖分化民眾同用唔合理既道德壓力去控制前線行動<br />\n<br />\n要解決其實好簡單 請培養你自己要有獨立思考既習慣 唔好見人地多正皮多AC係樓下撐就覺得一定係岩 <br />\n<br />\n請記住 係依個資訊流通極快既時代 做判斷前請依靠你自己既獨立思考 同埋記住只有你眼見既先係真實 道聽途說既只係資訊 只有經你獨立思考得出既結果先係你自己真正既諗法 唔好被人左右同控制你既思想 請大家好好咁思考一下你聽返黎既資訊係真定係假 係岩定係錯"},{"pid":"e5a562b35455a2e78925225e7d7983f78c318462","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"1 / 10"},{"pid":"05f3c0deb5aa7f78ac22fe8bed25c3f6b5be4ce3","tid":1631860,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"藍絲奶共狗開始不滿港共軍政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f70017aec411d583eb5d60efc8261779ad5d2569","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93e7fe4035840c479a7799f13aabf008332e100","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4e618455227a7aba75f2b46299d3f8661b79f3","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"唔好比連登依個革命基地淪陷 推"},{"pid":"a150f78917b1d6d3e6d28490c958288bd9e671cb","tid":1631860,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"77be6ff2e8259c76fe9e8d0a5a32720198ba80de","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9135d537d3ab7e9220d161a69ea04dbca3644ec","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78345bc116397d836a557b5629d046d78c09d23","tid":1631860,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5419bd1d332c02f7abd32864a14531b63105a834","tid":1631860,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"dfd1ae6fc7e07220644f3d51e9a9dd9f9bd44240","tid":1631860,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再參考連登的post , 眼見為正， 相信自己， 做自己認為正確嘅事就可以"},{"pid":"7cc9240d9025a875af4af4b17332e10ce70a8956","tid":1631860,"uid":279091,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"吊撚哂你哋D三毛係咁帶風向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家回帶7月1日:佢哋(義士)唔走，我哋都唔會走！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/692795324506293?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F692795324506293%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=59ce249e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/692795324506293?sfns=mo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n我哋點都唔會割 團結就是力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"df2203760d973b1191b2f71fe48933d14e3c6683","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"唔撚好再比D 風向撚同民意撚帶風向啦<br />\n<br />\n醒啦連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdd6996a1d934362fcb0960c7fa2b6ab44df553","tid":1631860,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae3d09422c81eab1462e19917de08a20a157706","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:59.000Z","msg":"唔撚好再比D 風向撚同民意撚帶風向啦<br />\n<br />\n醒啦連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f46175c0c3309c8675ec1ba89b12f1d2bc52d8d","tid":1631860,"uid":92,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"應付風向撚既方法 就是堅守自己立場"},{"pid":"161b5a5520b9e1a2d52be31d611882f7266a068e","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔撚好再比D 風向撚同民意撚帶風向啦<br />\n<br />\n醒啦連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15e3db9447517a68d1f8324ff6031c286785148","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"唔撚好再比D 風向撚同民意撚帶風向啦<br />\n<br />\n醒啦連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推啊屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b381be02006c3d9f9c8fab7a15bb2ec83d3ba55c","tid":1631860,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"re